        <p xml:lang="en">And after a space <name type="person">God</name> spake,  
        <lb/>and said to the Man, "Seeing that
        <lb/>I may not send thee to <name type="place">Hell</name>,
        <lb/>surely I shall send thee to  
        <lb/><name type="place">Heaven</name>. <del>Shall</del> Even unto <name type="place">Heaven</name> shall
